A large number of printed items in the scrapbooks are also duplicated in Series 8: Printed Matter. "Magazines, Periodicals" (No. 3), contains the following items: 
                        Life, March 1, 1948; 
                        Arts and Architecture, July 1951; 
                        Norte Revista Continental, Octubre 1942; 
                        Antiques, June 1952; and 
                        Horizons: Ukrainian Monthly of Literature, Arts, amd Critics, May 1951 (in Ukrainian). An additional scrapbook concerning the Archipenko School of Art is a part of Series 5: Teaching.
